snippet.title: The Quiet Lonely House Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a strange mansion in the outskirts of Delaware. Our main character, Danny Warson, is looking for his old friend Clive but this time what he uncovers is what he was expecting. A mansion full of strange things and creatures. Play the demo at https://klewis.itch.io/the-quiet-lonely-house

Credits:

"SCP-x5x (Outer Thoughts)" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
